1
00:00:58,117 --> 00:01:01,093
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:01,093 --> 00:01:03,063
=Episode 4=

3
00:01:03,063 --> 00:01:07,085
(Mute Husband)

4
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:18,199
Yuluo, you've become even prettier.

5
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,039
It's you.

6
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:21,719
Why are you so mean to me?

7
00:02:28,314 --> 00:02:32,719
(Gu Xuanji,
Second Young Miss of the Gu family)

8
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:34,599
Search carefully. Don't let them escape.

9
00:02:36,319 --> 00:02:39,280
My dear sister-in-law,
I'll let you handle it.

10
00:02:52,759 --> 00:02:53,560
How come it's you?

11
00:02:57,319 --> 00:02:59,280
Why are you so agitated, dear?

12
00:03:03,439 --> 00:03:04,479
Why are you here?

13
00:03:11,199 --> 00:03:12,120
It's chilly at night.

14
00:03:13,039 --> 00:03:14,560
You've been out for quite a while.

15
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:18,439
You said you and your husband
are deeply in love.

16
00:03:19,039 --> 00:03:21,919
He surely wouldn't
leave you out there alone.

17
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:25,080
Therefore, I brought you a cloak.

18
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:31,680
You don't have to act like this
when it's just the two of us.

19
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:36,240
But right now,
it's not just the two of us.

20
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:00,759
Yuluo.

21
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,520
Are you alright?

22
00:04:07,479 --> 00:04:09,719
Examine the bodies.
Take them to the authorities.

23
00:04:09,919 --> 00:04:10,719
- Understood.
- Understood.

24
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:16,399
Let's go find Xuanji.

25
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:39,600
Weren't you expecting
that molten iron flower show?

26
00:04:40,079 --> 00:04:43,120
If we miss it this time,
who knows when the next chance will be.

27
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:45,720
Take a look, young master.

28
00:04:50,519 --> 00:04:53,920
Yuluo, this suits you well.
Do you like it?

29
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:09,839
You have a keen eye.
This is a Yin-Yang Twin-Blade Dagger.

30
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:12,000
Press the gemstones.

31
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:15,759
Pressing the red gem ejects the blade.
Pressing the blue one retracts it.

32
00:05:16,079 --> 00:05:17,600
Only five taels of silver.

33
00:05:18,839 --> 00:05:21,519
What's so special about it?
Who gives a dagger to a woman?

34
00:05:39,079 --> 00:05:40,040
I like it very much.

35
00:05:47,319 --> 00:05:48,240
Thank you.

36
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:02,720
You're in a good mood.

37
00:06:03,199 --> 00:06:04,639
You were just being hunted down.

38
00:06:04,959 --> 00:06:07,240
Now you have the leisure to have tea?

39
00:06:08,199 --> 00:06:09,399
Thank you for saving me.

40
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:12,920
I toast to you.

41
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,519
Why were you there?

42
00:06:21,319 --> 00:06:23,800
I'm planning
to open a new tavern in the city.

43
00:06:23,959 --> 00:06:26,920
Zuixian Building happens to be
for transfer, so I took over.

44
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:30,079
I wanted to announce it
during the Lantern Festival.

45
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:32,399
But unfortunately, things went wrong.

46
00:06:33,519 --> 00:06:34,319
For transfer?

47
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:39,879
Yes, I heard the owner is going home
to get married a few days ago.

48
00:06:41,759 --> 00:06:43,920
Why did she have to
transfer the tavern for that?

49
00:06:44,879 --> 00:06:46,759
You seem quite concerned about her.

50
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:50,360
I just find it odd, that's all.

51
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:55,639
Speaking of which, when is your wedding?

52
00:06:58,680 --> 00:07:00,120
A storm is brewing.

53
00:07:03,199 --> 00:07:04,079
Let's set it for

54
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,879
one month from now.

55
00:07:09,199 --> 00:07:10,439
Zhaoxi's health condition...

56
00:07:12,079 --> 00:07:13,759
I can't wait that long.

57
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:16,600
You'll surely recover soon.

58
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,079
One more thing.

59
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:24,399
Master Zhaoxi
has just returned with injuries.

60
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,639
If anyone comes to visit...

61
00:07:27,759 --> 00:07:28,959
It's up to you.

62
00:07:30,439 --> 00:07:31,240
Understood.

63
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:41,600
In a month.

64
00:07:41,839 --> 00:07:42,639
What?

65
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:46,759
So soon?

66
00:07:47,319 --> 00:07:50,600
The original date
was nearly two months away.

67
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:52,240
In one month,

68
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:55,600
I'm not sure if my Nichang Workshop
can finish the garments.

69
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:58,240
Don't we have the wedding gown ready?

70
00:07:59,079 --> 00:08:02,600
Charging into the funeral hall
in your wedding gown was quite a tale.

71
00:08:02,959 --> 00:08:06,399
But it's better to replace it
since it's seen the funeral hall.

72
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:32,864
(Brother Gu Zhaoxi's Spirit Tablet)

73
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:39,600
No need.

74
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,759
So you refuse to accept my goodwill?

75
00:08:44,679 --> 00:08:45,559
That's not it.

76
00:08:49,279 --> 00:08:52,480
Let us get your measurements
for a new set of garments, Zhaoxi.

77
00:09:02,279 --> 00:09:05,120
In that case, we'll trouble you, Xuanji.

78
00:09:06,879 --> 00:09:08,159
Don't mention it, Yuluo.

79
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:10,960
Creating garments for a beauty
is a great pleasure.

80
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:15,360
But Zhaoxi, we haven't
seen each other for five years.

81
00:09:15,759 --> 00:09:18,559
How come you don't speak to me at all?

82
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:22,840
Do you disdain speaking
to an outsider like me?

83
00:09:40,799 --> 00:09:44,240
Zhaoxi, you haven't recovered yet.
It's all my fault.

84
00:09:44,279 --> 00:09:45,399
Let me take you back.

85
00:09:49,726 --> 00:09:51,328
(Wanfeng Pavilion, Gu Mansion)

86
00:10:23,039 --> 00:10:23,840
So,

87
00:10:24,679 --> 00:10:27,000
those assassins fled
into Xuanji's courtyard?

88
00:10:27,879 --> 00:10:31,559
Yes, but I didn't hear
any sounds of fighting.

89
00:10:31,759 --> 00:10:34,679
By the time I went for a closer look,
the assassins had vanished.

90
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:40,480
Are you saying
that Xuanji sent those assassins?

91
00:10:41,759 --> 00:10:43,279
Were they after Xuanji

92
00:10:44,399 --> 00:10:45,720
or that shop owner?

93
00:10:47,759 --> 00:10:48,759
I can't tell.

94
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:52,720
How is his wound?

95
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:53,519
Wound?

96
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:56,240
I asked him to take a medicinal bath.

97
00:10:57,279 --> 00:10:58,080
Reckless.

98
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:39,279
It's time?

99
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:47,440
Xuan Qing doesn't know
about your injury, but you do.

100
00:11:53,799 --> 00:11:54,944
Let me change your dressing.

101
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:20,720
Is this how you treat your husband too?

102
00:12:25,399 --> 00:12:29,240
Back when I was injured,
he comforted me like this.

103
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:33,000
This is a couple's thing.
You don't have to understand.

104
00:12:34,279 --> 00:12:36,080
Just focus on playing your part.

105
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:38,919
You did well today.

106
00:12:43,279 --> 00:12:44,120
A couple's thing.

107
00:12:51,399 --> 00:12:54,600
Barging in while someone is bathing

108
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:56,120
counts as a couple's thing?

109
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:02,759
I knocked.

110
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:04,399
Besides,

111
00:13:05,519 --> 00:13:07,000
if I hadn't barged in,

112
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:10,759
someone's wound would've festered.

113
00:13:15,039 --> 00:13:17,559
It occurs to me
that you're much more likable

114
00:13:18,519 --> 00:13:19,679
when you're quiet.

115
00:13:31,679 --> 00:13:34,440
Isn't that right, my mute husband?

116
00:13:38,879 --> 00:13:42,360
Tomorrow, I'll teach you
how to talk like him.

117
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,639
So many eyes on the Fufeng Pavilion.

118
00:13:58,720 --> 00:14:01,360
We've caught 13 people
and sent them for interrogation.

119
00:14:01,399 --> 00:14:03,799
But I may need to lie low for a while.

120
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:06,000
That courtyard guard has sharp hearing.

121
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:08,679
I tried sneaking in
and almost got caught several times.

122
00:14:11,960 --> 00:14:13,039
Got anything useful?

123
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:15,960
They're keeping tight-lipped.

124
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:19,080
But rest assured,
they'll crack in three days.

125
00:14:21,279 --> 00:14:22,120
Three days?

126
00:14:47,679 --> 00:14:48,480
Kill him.

127
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:51,759
I confess.

128
00:15:08,192 --> 00:15:11,168
(Watch the Fufeng Pavilion)

129
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:14,279
Master, what about these people?

130
00:15:15,440 --> 00:15:18,840
I never keep useless people around.
Dispose of them.

131
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:20,120
Understood.

132
00:15:28,720 --> 00:15:30,919
Why is that person
so fixated on Fufeng Pavilion?

133
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:34,559
But it seems
he's not siding with the Gu family.

134
00:15:35,039 --> 00:15:36,960
Forget about the spies
at Fufeng Pavilion.

135
00:15:37,440 --> 00:15:39,919
Stop patrolling the area for a few days.

136
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:42,399
Understood.

137
00:15:48,675 --> 00:15:50,272
(Fufeng Pavilion, Gu Mansion)

138
00:15:56,480 --> 00:15:58,240
Things have quieted down these days.

139
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:01,000
You haven't spotted any spies?

140
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:02,639
None.

141
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:05,519
Though someone has been
lingering outside.

142
00:16:05,960 --> 00:16:07,440
Exceptional lightness skills.

143
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:11,440
I haven't been able to
track him down yet.

144
00:16:12,320 --> 00:16:16,279
Since my "husband" arrived,
I've had much more free time.

145
00:16:20,159 --> 00:16:22,440
Seems I should pay him a visit.

146
00:16:54,208 --> 00:16:56,736
(Vast Mind, Eternal Will)

147
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:14,000
Is this how you knocked yesterday?

148
00:17:14,759 --> 00:17:17,039
Why did you come so early today?

149
00:17:18,480 --> 00:17:22,200
Didn't I tell you
I'd teach you how to speak?

150
00:17:39,319 --> 00:17:42,759
To imitate someone
is not just to look like them.

151
00:17:43,559 --> 00:17:44,519
It requires observation.

152
00:17:45,759 --> 00:17:48,680
Imitate their moves,
vocal patterns, and speech mannerisms

153
00:17:49,119 --> 00:17:51,400
in the shortest time possible.

154
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:55,799
But you've never met Zhaoxi.

155
00:17:56,440 --> 00:17:59,319
So you can only rely on my descriptions.

156
00:18:01,599 --> 00:18:06,799
In that case, you must
avoid people to stay safe.

157
00:18:18,599 --> 00:18:19,480
Like this.

158
00:18:30,440 --> 00:18:31,920
Zhaoxi has always been ill.

159
00:18:32,519 --> 00:18:36,240
Temperatures bearable for most people
would burn him.

160
00:18:37,599 --> 00:18:40,680
So hold the tea saucer
when accepting tea.

161
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:42,752
That's your first lesson.

162
00:18:43,039 --> 00:18:47,359
Finish the tea, then I'll teach you
how to talk like him.

163
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:18,799
I was going to ask you
to blow on it and sip slowly.

164
00:19:19,680 --> 00:19:21,480
But you're quick to improvise.

165
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:34,440
Dear.

166
00:19:48,799 --> 00:19:49,759
Your hairpin is crooked.

167
00:19:55,359 --> 00:19:57,119
What's wrong, dear?

168
00:20:06,720 --> 00:20:07,599
Nothing.

169
00:20:08,519 --> 00:20:10,839
It's just that since you arrived,

170
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:13,759
things have quieted down
in this courtyard.

171
00:20:16,640 --> 00:20:19,799
Now let me teach you
how to speak like Zhaoxi.

172
00:20:29,279 --> 00:20:31,440
Keep your voice light, not too deep.

173
00:21:11,397 --> 00:21:16,460
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

174
00:21:16,997 --> 00:21:22,318
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

175
00:21:22,885 --> 00:21:29,513
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

176
00:21:29,513 --> 00:21:34,277
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

177
00:21:34,277 --> 00:21:36,613
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

178
00:21:36,613 --> 00:21:43,313
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

179
00:21:43,313 --> 00:21:50,085
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

180
00:21:50,085 --> 00:21:57,221
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

181
00:21:57,221 --> 00:22:01,605
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

182
00:22:01,605 --> 00:22:04,229
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

183
00:22:04,229 --> 00:22:10,863
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

184
00:22:10,863 --> 00:22:17,413
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

185
00:22:17,413 --> 00:22:24,537
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

186
00:22:24,627 --> 00:22:28,997
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

187
00:22:28,997 --> 00:22:31,705
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

188
00:22:31,705 --> 00:22:37,605
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

189
00:22:38,245 --> 00:22:44,233
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

